description: Demolition of existing structures.  Erection of mixed use building ranging from six to nine storeys with commercial use at ground floor and 55 residential units above.  With associated landscaping, amenity space, car parking, cycle and refuse storage.  (summary)
decision_conditions:
The development hereby permitted shall be begun no later than the  expiration of three years from the date of this permission.

Reason: In order to comply with the requirements of Section 91 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.
